imageDescription: A disco ball spinning in a dark room, casting glittering reflections on the wet floor. The ball is surrounded by shattered glass, symbolizing the brokenness and chaos of the dance floor. The image captures the energy and intensity of the song, with the disco ball representing the pulsating beats and the shattered glass reflecting the lyrics of "heads will roll."
